nodes.text: Legacy 35: Storms, Part 2 is the thirty-fifth issue of the Star Wars: Legacy comic series and the second issue in the Storms story arc.

The fallout from the battle on Had Abbadon is being felt throughout the galaxy. On Coruscant, Moffs Nyna Calixte and Morlish Veed contemplate the news and wonder what it means for their plans to rule the Empire; while across the galaxy, deposed Emperor Roan Fel mourns what has been lost.
Meanwhile "Bantha" Rawk aids Cade in a dangerous plan to save a friend. The conclusion to "Storms" will set a new path for Legacy—the galaxy has been reborn . . . again!
When Cade Skywalker is fighting the Uggli Brothers, a wall behind them is covered in Aurebesh graffiti, which has no actual meaning. Some of the symbols are not even Aurebesh.
